{
  "id": "S2R2N207",
  "title": {
    "product_var": "ZPRODTSK",
    "text": "EDIT PRIMARY COMMAND - REDO",
    "version_var": "ZSHRTVER",
    "prefix": "HELP"
  },
  "type": "menu",
  "body": {
    "rows": [
      {
        "type": "command",
        "variable": "ZCMD"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Purpose"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Specifies that one or more EDIT operations which were undone should"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "be re-done. This is the opposite of UNDO."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Format"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "REDO [ nnn | ALL ]"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Remarks"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "In the normal use of EDIT you will make numerous changes to a file."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "When UNDO processing is on, each change is recorded in a journal which"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "may subsequently be used to undo a change. Having undone a change, you"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "may want to redo it. This is when the REDO command comes into play."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "For each UNDO with no intervening changes, you can apply REDO. If no"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "parameters are specified, only the last posted UNDO is redone."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "If a number is specified, REDO is applied to the specific number of"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "posted UNDOs. In the event that the posted number of UNDOs is smaller"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "than the specified number, only the posted UNDOs are redone."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "field_row",
        "fields": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "(Hit"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "ENTER+to return to previous menu)"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
